  "body": [
    "Bhai Arjan Singh Matharu’s voice will always be immortalized in the Asa Di Vaar recording of Bhai Surjan Singh Ji which has to be one of the most popular Asa Di Vaar recordings of all time. Bhai Arjan Singh Ji accompanied Bhai Surjan Singh Ji for many years along with Bhai Prem Singh Ji on tabla. Most of these recordings below were contributed by Dr. Manjit Singh Hunjin, who refers to Bhai Arjan Singh Ji as ‘Mama Ji’. If anyone has more recordings of Bhai Sahib Ji to share, please contact us.",
    "This huge collection of recordings were contributed by Dr. Manjit Singh Hunjin, who is a very talented artist. Please check out his Instagram page at the following link https://www.instagram.com/amsimeetart/?hl=en"
  ],
